<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/8169> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #8169" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut., or pr.? 89. In MRR 2.36 and 39, note 21, refer also to Diod. 37.2.8.[76]\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4348> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4348" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul in Illyricum (see 78, Promagistrates)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4320> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4320" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul in Illyricum (see 78, Promagistrates)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4294> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4294" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Proconsul in Illyrieum, where he occupied portions of the Dalmatian coast, and captured Salonae after two years of campaigning (Cic. Cluent. 97; Eutrop. 6.4; Oros. 5.23.23; of. Sall. Hist. 2.39-40M; Val. Max. 8. 1, abs. 8)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4293> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4293" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "4 Münzer's identification of Cosconius with the commander in Apulia in 89 seems very probable (RE), but the precise date of his command in Illyricum remains uncertain. War there probably began in 78 and ended in 76 (Eutrop. 6. 1. 1; 6.4). It had certainly ended before 74, when M. Atilius Bulbus, who was convicted of maiestas for tampering with the legions of Cosconius (Cic.), served as a juror in the trial of Oppianicus (Cic. Cluent. 71-72 and 97; Verr. 1.39)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3939> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3939" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Held command in Apulia where he reduced a series of towns, including Venusia, and the tribe of the Pediculi (Liv. Per. 75; App. BC 1.52)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3938> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3938" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "21 In Appian he title of Cosconius is #. He is almost certainly the Cosconius who was Proconsul in 77 or 76 in Illyricum, and whose praetorship would normally have preceded that command by only a year. See 78, Pro-magistrates." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3898> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3898" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "See Legates, and note 9." .
